178
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:04,500
[SPEAKER_01] Osoba koja sam nekad prije bio.

179
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:07,500
[SPEAKER_01] Gangster koji sam nekad prije bio.

180
00:16:07,500 --> 00:16:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ja više ni ne znam koja je ta osoba.

181
