185
00:16:36,299 --> 00:16:40,299
[SPEAKER_00] Osoba koja je izlječena.

186
00:16:40,299 --> 00:16:43,299
[SPEAKER_01] Osoba koja je slobodna.

187
00:16:43,299 --> 00:16:45,899
